Package: amber
Type: Package
Title: Local-First Web-Page Capture (AmberHTML)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("AmberHTML Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: R bindings for AmberHTML, a local-first web-page capture engine.
    Wraps the amber-core C ABI via .Call to capture pages as Markdown, readable
    text, single-file HTML, MHTML, WARC/WACZ, PDF, or a screenshot. The native
    amber-core library must be staged before building (see generate.sh).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/afeique/amber-html
